# Financial Risk Credit Eligible Collateral Rebate Investment Risk Charge Amount

## identifier
de8811

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of investment risk charge rebate in relation to eligible collateral provided to the reporting party, as determined in accordance with relevant prudential standard.

Eligible collateral includes any form of security that supports the value of assets held by the reporting party other than guarantees and letters of credit.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=FinancialRisk.Credit.EligibleCollateralRebateInvestmentRiskCharge.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.06
- period=instant
